  "texts": [
    "First, CircDA constructs heterogeneous features for multisource biological data.",
    "Then, CircDA uses the variable fusion feature inference network GNNq for feature inference and the label propagation network GNNp for label propagation.",
    "The two graph autoencoders are trained end-to-end using the variational EM algorithm.",
    "GMNN alternating training based on variational inference enhances CircDA's ability to obtain efficient high-dimensional representation.",
    "CircDA proposed in this study achieved satisfactory results in circRNA-disease association prediction."
